<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Glenbrook</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1958, Glenbrook is bound by the Sarcee Trail on the west, the Richmond Road on the south, 37 Street W on the east and 26 Avenue S on the north.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The few residential units that date back to the 60s have been recently renovated and remodeled to cater to the needs of the modern lifestyle and are available at anywhere between $200,000 and $750,000. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">From cozy ranch-style bungalows to contemporary duplexes, there is something for everyone in this family-friendly neighborhood. </p>
        </div>
